id: pm-atfm
title: "Context relevance evaluation harness: graded golden-workspace judgments for pm context/next quality"
description: "Evaluation harness for context quality: graded workspaces and continuity scenarios that measure whether pm context/next return the right items under explicit token budgets."
type: Feature
