  "2026-07-06T23:51:08.193Z",codex-agent,"Planning evidence 2026-07-07: pm-atfm remains the canonical quality harness for context/next relevance. Added non-duplicate child slices pm-lixy (graded scenario corpus across scratch, real-shaped, scale, and returning-agent continuity cases) and pm-xmp5 (offline runner + CI gate). Done definition should mirror search-eval rigor but score context assembly: rank-aware quality, required-item recall, continuity-delta coverage, and token-budget adherence. This keeps pm-4k6b weight tuning evidence-driven instead of aesthetic.\n"
  "2026-07-09T19:10:26.051Z",codex-root-20260709,"Progress evidence: context/next evaluation harness now has public SDK runner contracts, reviewable golden workspaces, committed baseline, required CI gate, and documented intentional-update workflow."
  "2026-07-09T19:50:43.336Z",codex-root-20260709,"Verification: public SDK evaluation scenario/corpus APIs execute context and next through real PmClient readers with attribution and threshold/baseline regression reporting. Four committed scenarios and installed-package consumer pass; thresholds remain explicit and token budgets measured from compact payloads."
  "2026-07-09T23:53:29.316Z",codex-root-20260709,"Handoff after PR #487: the typed relevance evaluator, scenario-level regression gate, SDK/package exports, CLI explainability, docs, and exact 100% coverage are merged and green on e953bdcb. Item remains in_progress because the explicitly scoped 10k/100k representative corpus and performance study are not yet complete."
  "2026-07-10T00:03:04.613Z",codex-root-20260709,"Post-merge Gemini review follow-up: validate every required corpus threshold as a finite number before executing the external JSON evaluation gate. Review thread: discussion_r3555533556."
  "2026-07-10T00:16:51.550Z",codex-root-20260709,"Review-fix evidence: the external corpus reader now rejects missing, null, NaN/non-finite required thresholds with metric-specific errors before workspace setup. Focused gate tests and the real committed corpus pass; full suite remains exact 100% coverage."
  "2026-07-10T05:53:29.680Z",codex-root-20260709,"Verification evidence 2026-07-10: full sandbox suite passed 270 files / 5,505 tests with exact 100% statements, branches, functions, and lines. pm test-all over the seven active items passed 8 linked commands with 0 failures and 1 duplicate-safe skip. pnpm typecheck, contracts:check, lint (ESLint + 0 jscpd clones + static quality/token budget), docs-skills, context-eval, security scan, and audit all passed. Live CodeFactor reports A+ and 0 issues. Fresh packed npm install at /tmp/pm-cli-sdk-path-proof-XIsSsh activated 11 bundled packages in a path-target tracker, left caller extension files at zero, and passed CLI/SDK context plus isolated doctor with zero blocking failures. pm health is clean and history drift is zero."
